  </section>

  <!-- Company Policies -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-space font-bold gradient-text mb-4">Company Policies</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Our commitment to creating a positive, inclusive, and productive work environment
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197m13.5-9a2.5 2.5 0 11-5 0 2.5 2.5 0 015 0z"></path>
              </svg>
              Diversity & Inclusion
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
              We are committed to fostering a diverse and inclusive workplace where everyone feels valued, respected, and empowered to contribute their best work.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
              <li>• Equal opportunity employment practices</li>
              <li>• Zero tolerance for discrimination or harassment</li>
              <li>• Inclusive hiring and promotion processes</li>
              <li>• Regular diversity and inclusion training</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-400 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
              </svg>
              Data Privacy & Security
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
              We maintain the highest standards of data protection and cybersecurity to safeguard our clients' information and our intellectual property.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
              <li>• GDPR and CCPA compliance</li>
              <li>• Regular security audits and assessments</li>
              <li>• Employee security training programs</li>
              <li>• Secure development practices</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-400 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
              </svg>
              Professional Development
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
              We invest in our team's growth through continuous learning opportunities, skill development programs, and career advancement support.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
              <li>• Annual learning and development budget</li>
              <li>• Conference and workshop attendance</li>
              <li>• Internal mentorship programs</li>
              <li>• Certification and training support</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-400 mr-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
              </svg>
              Work-Life Balance
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
              We believe that a healthy work-life balance is essential for both personal well-being and professional success.
            </p>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400">
              <li>• Flexible working hours and remote options</li>
              <li>• Generous vacation and personal time off</li>
              <li>• Mental health and wellness programs</li>
              <li>• Family-friendly policies and benefits</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Partners Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-gray-800/50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-space font-bold gradient-text mb-4">Our Partners</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          We collaborate with industry leaders to deliver comprehensive solutions
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 hover:border-blue-500 transition-all duration-300 hover-glow text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-cyan-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 3v2m6-2v2M9 19v2m6-2v2M5 9H3m2 6H3m18-6h-2m2 6h-2M7 19h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2zM9 9h6v6H9V9z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Technology Partners</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            Strategic partnerships with leading cloud providers, AI platforms, and software vendors to deliver cutting-edge solutions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 hover:border-blue-500 transition-all duration-300 hover-glow text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-teal-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Industry Partners</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            Collaborations with organizations across various industries to understand sector-specific challenges and requirements.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gray-900/50 backdrop-blur-sm p-8 rounded-xl border border-gray-700 hover:border-blue-500 transition-all duration-300 hover-glow text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
            <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3">Academic Partners</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-400">
            Partnerships with universities and research institutions to stay at the forefront of technological advancement and innovation.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Partner Logos Placeholder -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">Trusted by leading organizations worldwide</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 lg:grid-cols-6 gap-8 items-center opacity-60">
          {Array.from({length: 6}).map((_, i) => (
            <div class="bg-gray-800 h-16 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-gray-500 font-semibold">Partner {i + 1}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>


    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Location Section -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-space font-bold gradient-text mb-4">Our Location</h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Headquartered in the heart of the tech innovation district
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-gray-800 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-700">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Headquarters</h3>
            
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-400 mr-4 mt-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path>
